text: Dadang Wigiarto (20 December 1966 - 26 November 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was a member of the National Awakening Party. Wigiarto was born in Pasuruan, Indonesia. From 2010 until his death, he was Regent of the Situbondo Regency. Wigiarto died of COVID-19 on 26 November 2020 in the Situbondo Regency at the age of 53.Terpapar Corona, Bupati Situbondo Meninggal Dunia ==References== Category:1966 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Indonesia Category:Indonesian politicians
